reviewText:
Good Dvd. Like those old good quality shows. Sonny and Cher
were fantastic.
The last of the lavish variety shows - Sonny was much funnier than he was given credit for - and Cher looks incredible doing some of her biggest hits.  Lots of silly humor.
If you already own the DVD Box Set then you already own this episode!  If you are just curious to see what The Sonny & Cher show was, then by all means by this today!
